<item>
            <title>[PIG-4798] big integer and big decimal literals fail to parse</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4798</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For example:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;x &amp;lt; 12345678901234567890&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;with x being a biginteger tries to parse the literal as Integer. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;x &amp;lt; 12345678901234567890BI&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&quot;BI&quot; is not recognized&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12937405">PIG-4798</key>
            <summary>big integer and big decimal literals fail to parse</summary>
